4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would require the Public Service
6 Commission to hold meetings at least annually regarding
7 the regulation of utilities and other topics within the
8 commission's powers and duties.
9 This bill would require notice of the meetings
10 in compliance with the Alabama Open Meetings Act.
11 This bill would provide for the impeachment of
12 commissioners if a meeting is not held or notice of the
13 meeting is not provided.
14 This bill would also prohibit an electric
15 utility from including costs incurred by the utility
16 and related to giving grants, lobbying, or advertising
17 for the utility from being included in the
18 determination of a schedule for rates or service
19 regulations.
20
21
